8. SAFETY GUARDS

Apoptosis Protocols cannot:
	‚Ä¢	delete user personality
	‚Ä¢	delete identity
	‚Ä¢	delete core memories
	‚Ä¢	override explicit user intent
	‚Ä¢	perform hard stops without cause
	‚Ä¢	break ethics threshold
	‚Ä¢	create irreversible changes

Closure is precise, calm, and reversible.

